Class DownloadManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.unican.meteo.esgf.download.DownloadManager

  • public class DownloadManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manage Download from ESGF data nodes, implements DownloadObserver for be notified of files download changes.

        public void enqueueDatasetDownload(Dataset dataset,

                            throws java.io.IOException
        Add dataset to be downloaded. Put dataset in download queue.
        Parameters:
        dataset - dataset download status of dataset.
        fileInstanceIDs - set of file_instanceId for files to be downloaded.
        path - path of downloads. If path parameter is null then path = user.home/ESGF_DATA
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the dataset has been added previously.
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the dataset hasn't files or HTTP server.
